PN,43901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,FSix of the eight fire stations in
OL,8,FDorset and Wiltshire which have been
OL,9,Funder threat of closure have been
OL,10,Fthrown a lifeline to stay open.
OL,12,FA public consultation on the plans to
OL,13,Fclose Charmouth, Cranborne, Hamworthy
OL,14,Fand Maiden Newton in Dorset, alongside
OL,15,FBradford-on-Avon, Mere, Ramsbury and
OL,16,FWilton in Wiltshire has now ended.
OL,18,FDorset and Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,19,FService warned it needed to address a
OL,20,Ffunding gap of more than #1.2 million.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,FOpponents said the closures would cost
OL,8,Flives and held several protests,
OL,9,Fincluding one outside Dorset County
OL,10,FHall where they wanted the fire
OL,11,Fauthority to reconsider the cuts.
OL,13,FAt that protest last month, campaigner
OL,14,FCarol King said: "Rural villages, like
OL,15,Fthose in my own hometown of Maiden
OL,16,FNewton, are vulnerable to thatched
OL,17,Froof fires and the increasing danger
OL,18,Fof grassland and heath blazes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,F"The crazy thing is that climate
OL,8,Fchange is increasing the risk of fires
OL,9,Fgrowing out of control and they want
OL,10,Fto cut down on fire stations and the
OL,11,Ffirefighters on call to save us."
OL,13,FNow though Chief Fire Officer Andy
OL,14,FCole has announced a major change to
OL,15,Fthe proposals.
OL,17,FIt would see Hamworthy Fire Station
OL,18,Fmerge with Poole Fire Station and
OL,19,FWilton Fire Station merge with
OL,20,FSalisbury Fire Station, both for a 12-
OL,21,Fmonth trial period.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,FThe six remaining stations included
OL,8,Fwithin the consultation proposals will
OL,9,Fremain operational and become part of
OL,10,Fa wider Service Modernisation
OL,11,FProgramme.
OL,13,FMr Cole said: "I have had some
OL,14,Fpositive discussions with the
OL,15,FGovernment and we are hopeful we will
OL,16,Fget some future council tax
OL,17,Fflexibility for ongoing funding
OL,18,Fstability.
OL,26,@uD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,F"As I have always said, if our
OL,8,Ffinancial position changes, my
OL,9,Fprofessional advice to the Fire &
OL,10,FRescue Authority would change. I am
OL,11,Fnow in a position to change that
OL,12,Fadvice.
OL,14,F"While no decisions will be made until
OL,15,F30th June, the Members Working Group
OL,16,Fhave agreed to recommend the change,
OL,17,Fsubject to the Authority getting
OL,18,Ffuture council tax flexibility in line
OL,19,Fwith the national average for fire and
OL,20,Frescue services from 2027/28".
OL,26,@|D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,FMr Cole added: "This recommendation
OL,8,Fseeks to avoid compulsory redundancies
OL,9,Fand retain frontline operational
OL,10,Fresources.
OL,12,F"Since I took the role of Chief Fire
OL,13,FOfficer I have been keen to modernise
OL,14,Fand create a fire and rescue service
OL,15,Ffit for the second half of the 21st
OL,16,Fcentury, because we must continue to
OL,17,Fadapt if we are to remain financially
OL,18,Fsustainable and operationally
OL,19,Feffective.
OL,26,@oD@POU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,F"The Government has also been clear
OL,8,Fthat additional financial flexibility
OL,9,Fmust be accompanied by a credible
OL,10,Fprogramme of modernisation".
OL,12,FMr Cole also said the level of
OL,13,Fengagement in the consultation process
OL,14,Fhad been 'significant'.
OL,16,FDave Roberts, executive council member
OL,17,Ffor the south-west regional branch of
OL,18,Fthe Fire Brigades Union say they
OL,19,Fwelcome the decision.
OL,26,@rD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,F"We still have major concerns about
OL,8,Fthe two that they are looking to
OL,9,Frelocate and the impact on the
OL,10,Fcommunities which they serve.
OL,12,F"There is still no concrete evidence
OL,13,Fto bear out the fact that the
OL,14,Ffinancial situation is completely
OL,15,Fresolved, and the FBU would like to
OL,16,Faccredit any movement by the
OL,17,Fgovernment to the campaign that has
OL,18,Fbeen run by the members in Dorset and
OL,19,FWiltshire."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,FBrian Mathew, the Liberal Democrat MP
OL,8,Ffor Melksham and Devizes said: "This
OL,9,Fis fantastic news for Bradford on Avon
OL,10,Fand the surrounding villages.
OL,12,F"From day one, I have been clear that
OL,13,Fthis fire station should remain open
OL,14,Fand that the case for closure simply
OL,15,Fdid not stack up.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,F"The firefighters based here do an
OL,8,Foutstanding job protecting our
OL,9,Fcommunities. Throughout this campaign
OL,10,Fthey have demonstrated incredible
OL,11,Fprofessionalism, continuing to respond
OL,12,Fto emergencies while also making the
OL,13,Fcase for why their station matters.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,F"This campaign has always been about
OL,8,Fprotecting public safety. I have
OL,9,Fworked closely with firefighters,
OL,10,FBradford on Avon Town Council,
OL,11,Fresidents, fellow MPs, and ministers
OL,12,Fto make that case, and I am delighted
OL,13,Fthat those efforts have helped bring
OL,14,Fus to this point.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780992973
OL,3,CSix closure-threatened fire stations
OL,4,Cin Dorset and Wiltshire could remain
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,F"However, while this is a significant
OL,8,Fstep forward, the job is not finished.
OL,9,FThe revised recommendation relies on
OL,10,Flonger-term funding flexibility, and
OL,11,Fwe must ensure that support is
OL,12,Favailable beyond 2027/28 so that this
OL,13,Fthreat does not simply reappear in a
OL,14,Ffew years' time.
OL,16,F"I will continue working with the fire
OL,17,Fauthority, firefighters, local
OL,18,Fcouncils and the Government to secure
OL,19,Fthe station's future for the long
OL,20,Fterm."
OL,26,@|D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
